data.description: Bells and Whistles galore! 4 BD 3 BA home in desirable Lake Asbury Southbank community.   Upgraded flooring, kitchen appliances and granite counter tops, hurricane shutters on back sliding glass doors. Garage has privacy screen that can keep out the bugs  Separate ensuite with a separate entrance and handicap shower.  Large great room and separate dining/living room.  Brand new roof in 2022.  Amenities include children's park and a gated pool for Silver Creek Community.
